**Overview**

This dashboard provides a centralized view of security findings from AWS GuardDuty. It visualizes data based on severity levels, regions, and resource types, allowing teams to assess potential threats in their cloud environments. Summary metrics help highlight the overall volume and severity of findings, while time-series and categorical breakdowns assist in identifying trends and common threat sources. Filters can be used to refine the results by cloud provider, region, or account for more focused investigations.
